= Required packages =
ArchLinux
 * pymacs
 * auctex
 * emacs-haskell-mode
 * slime
 * emacs-color-theme
 * emacs-jabber
 * mercurial

Ubuntu
 * emacs-goodies-el
 * auctex
 * emacs-jabber
 * python-mode
 * emms
 * libtagc0-dev

= Installation =
== Install cedet ==
$ emacs -Q -l cedet-build.el -f cedet-build

== Install jabber ==
 autoreconf -i
 ./configure && make

== Emacs Muse ==
For LaTeX mathematical equations, install tetex-extra and dvipng packages.
